00:02:18,895 --> 00:02:35,939
And that gives them a huge advantage in negotiations. If we want more commercial development, responsible residential development, community benefits agreements that provide millions of dollars in fees to help fund the important things that our city needs, and just affordable homes for working families and people who want to stay here, we need a plan.

