9
00:03:30,732 --> 00:03:54,020
The city and our elected officials also need to do a better job of communicating and engaging residents in big decisions that affect them. That's why I'll hold regular public office hours and invite residents to review city council meeting agendas and materials before the meeting so we can decide what we want to do. It's also why we need new city and school websites. Has anyone been on any of our websites recently? So residents and families can find the information they need.

10
00:03:54,121 --> 00:04:05,478
